{"tid":1421221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位佛教徒示威者","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:41:53.000Z","uid":254209,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4546acf7cb7ceb8b28c4fe012eaf5b24935cbbd6","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"面對住示威場地如此困難既境，我地仍然要保持住平靜既心，唔好俾瞋心控制住自己。<br />\n可以嘗試係示威時念下心經同六字大明咒，平靜過再稍稍安撫身邊既戰友，認清目標。相信大家身邊既朋友都一直處於非常緊張同難受既狀態，自身平靜先能夠幫助到身邊既人。<br />\n<br />\nJohn Lennon：「當抗爭向暴力升級，你便墮入建制的把戲內。當權者會不惜一切地惹怒你，拉扯你的髮鬚，搧你的耳光，引誘你動粗。只要將你迫為暴徒，他們便有方法收拾你。唯一令當權者束手無策的，是非暴力與幽默。」<br />\n<br />\n加油!<br />\n<br />\n利申: 發夢自己係前線一邊念六字大明咒一邊滅摧淚彈"},{"pid":"ca567feda3a71de08a4936820b1a7927aa50839e","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9afe46e21bdabeff96d7e09cb49e95f39fa1e5f","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"c80c386f8403abb914eef5fcee8661ff698d4998","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"35f1ebaeeefecfc4c68ac0571a94929825f17758","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"8333b9e5625d8792c5585c379060f509cea10705","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"9000aeb9c781783e0ab0ccffa8b56daeeaf79653","tid":1421221,"uid":254209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:32:53.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推"},{"pid":"3cfc8770ca241a833c8872958dbc69ea2d9eb923","tid":1421221,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"念佛號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 䆁加如來"}]}